'''Bosph wanderers''' were [[Bosph (species)|Bosph]] who traveled [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] in the pursuit of knowledge [[Millennium/Legends|thousands of years]] prior to the decline of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. Their legacy, the [[way of the traveler]], was embraced by the few Bosph that remained during the rise of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] and the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

